{"tid":1963684,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「限聚令」延長至4月23日","createTime":"2020-04-08T10:07:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T12:02:56.000Z","uid":19055,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c9b263d704172ad6234d867d867b85b49f3eb7a7","tid":1963684,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T10:07:20.000Z","msg":"政府早上宣布，「限聚令」延長至4月23日。早前要求停業的遊戲機中心、浴室、健身中心、遊樂場所、卡拉OK場所等，亦須再延長停業至本月23日。另外新增兩大場所需要關閉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一、規管餐飲業務<br />\n<br />\n在任何時間均不得超過該處所通常座位數目的50%<br />\n桌子擺放布局最少有1.5米距離或設有某種形式的隔板作出有效分隔<br />\n不得有多於4人同坐一桌<br />\n除飲食外，須一直佩戴口罩<br />\n進入餐廳前，須先為食客量度體溫<br />\n提供消毒潔手液<br />\n不得提供酒類飲品<br />\n<br />\n二、延長指定場所關閉時間<br />\n遊戲機中心<br />\n浴室<br />\n健身中心<br />\n遊樂場所<br />\n公眾娛樂場所<br />\n供租用舉行社交聚會的處所（一般稱為派對房間）<br />\n夜店或夜總會<br />\n卡拉OK場所<br />\n麻將天九耍樂處所<br />\n按摩院（新增項目）<br />\n美容院（新增項目）<br />\n<br />\n繼續假防疫，真打壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f343b01fdf8fe3912299c9084de8a8bf38ceeec","tid":1963684,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T10:07:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好意思，好怕大家忘記了，可唔可以入嚟幫手推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n［5個月］［整合］大家記唔記得今日係咩日子<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1963297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1963297</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/08/171441_9b725230f319dbfd347dc84fa175d02e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F08%2F171441_9b725230f319dbfd347dc84fa175d02e.png&h=bb404f5b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5321b58264eaddf7b2af4f2b11bc17953958b12d","tid":1963684,"uid":79793,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T10:08:53.000Z","msg":"個感覺好神奇，呢一年好似啲打機活動咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一樣完左又黎多樣"},{"pid":"eec17f7f04ea1dd52e6f180d6feeb14d9b7f82bb","tid":1963684,"uid":42804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5321b58264eaddf7b2af4f2b11bc17953958b12d","tid":1963684,"uid":79793,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T10:08:53.000Z","msg":"個感覺好神奇，呢一年好似啲打機活動咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一樣完左又黎多樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T10:10:36.000Z","msg":"會一直禁，禁到六月尾，到時會永續。"},{"pid":"9fadf62670c4b44dddf93611bb181a12ec30c223","tid":1963684,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T10:10:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c2fe5496c4fdc1665721aae70bf960b2c6a6061","tid":1963684,"uid":33216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T10:13:18.000Z","msg":"除飲食外，咁飲品到可除口罩？"},{"pid":"b3c6aa69d6c3dd9c4643f757dbd48be37199bdb0","tid":1963684,"uid":2455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T11:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94234427e87af110a3196ee29439bb03e07ebcb","tid":1963684,"uid":61330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T11:03:05.000Z","msg":"唔比人開係咪想人地執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6083f9f4a11104261acae5c9247f3135ac2a157a","tid":1963684,"uid":221346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T11:04:27.000Z","msg":"有撚用咩 出街仲見到成班廢老聚賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又冇人捉"},{"pid":"8f68322e0c5084b8190f56b4ea56b40968572866","tid":1963684,"uid":250356,"like":1,"dislike":